    <summary>Drive more sales to your store through your customers&#x2019; social networks. Sign up for a free trial now!</summary>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Advocado helps you drive more sales through your customers' social networks. It incentivizes your customers to refer your business to their friends.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&#xD;
&lt;p&gt;It has 2 key features:&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&#xD;
&lt;ol&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li&gt;Offer an instant discount to encourage social sharing&lt;br /&gt; Give your customers an instant discount at checkout when they share your products on their social networks. This generates greater branding and awareness for your business.&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li&gt;(Coming soon) Further reward your customers with a promo code to drive more sales.&lt;br /&gt;When your customers successfully refer a purchasing customer (or MORE) to you, you further reward your customers and their referred friends with a promo code. The more friends join in and buy from you, the greater the value of cashback you give to all of them.&#xD;
&lt;/ol&gt;&#xD;
&#xD;
&#xD;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;ol&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li /&gt;Ditch troublesome advertising dollars - Save time and money spent on creating an extensive online advertising effort with our easy to install plugin.&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li&gt;Get people to talk about your brand - Turn your customers into your loyal advocates and create word-of-mouth-advertising that is trusted&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li&gt;Generate more referrals - Reward your customers for every successful referral they make and drive more sales for your business.&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;
&lt;li&gt;Easy to set up - You can install our plugin or copy &amp; paste a snippet of codes to get Advocado up and running. Our set up wizard will guide you through this.&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description>
    <notes>We've introduced a new mechanic to this extension. It does not allow double-dipping --  if a shopper gets an instant discount, they should not be able to redeem a coupon code for the same cart.&#xD;
&#xD;
You can sign up for an account immediately after you register. Do let us know if you have any feedback or comments either through our website http://getadvocado.com, or via our email: dax@getadvocado.com</notes>
